  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can't beat this game!!! Super Hipster Lumberjack is a love letter to the era of difficult online flash platformers. This cheap double feature includes the original highschool project by Noah that released in 2015. Along with a remastered version of the game released in 2025.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/388340/extras/03e45de7ad03676296dbe06c0d8dfc66.poster.avif?t=1752696046\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/388340/extras/03e45de7ad03676296dbe06c0d8dfc66.webm?t=1752696046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/388340/extras/03e45de7ad03676296dbe06c0d8dfc66.mp4?t=1752696046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > In this story Noah attempts to make a game for the first time. He is then trapped in his own creation. He learns that making games is a lot harder than he thought. Use your axe to traverse a mess of your own mind's design! To beat this game you'll need precision platforming and experimention with jump techniques. Are you up to the task?</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You can't beat this game!!! Super Hipster Lumberjack is a love letter to the era of difficult online flash platformers. This cheap double feature includes the original highschool project by Noah that released in 2015. Along with a remastered version of the game released in 2025.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/388340/extras/03e45de7ad03676296dbe06c0d8dfc66.poster.avif?t=1752696046\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/388340/extras/03e45de7ad03676296dbe06c0d8dfc66.webm?t=1752696046\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/388340/extras/03e45de7ad03676296dbe06c0d8dfc66.mp4?t=1752696046\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > In this story Noah attempts to make a game for the first time. He is then trapped in his own creation. He learns that making games is a lot harder than he thought. Use your axe to traverse a mess of your own mind's design! To beat this game you'll need precision platforming and experimention with jump techniques. Are you up to the task?</p>",
